- Use React 18 with Next.js 15 App Router and prefer Server Components when fetching data.
- Style exclusively with TailwindCSS utility classes plus shadcn/ui primitives. Avoid custom CSS files unless unavoidable.
- Prefer Radix UI components (`@radix-ui/react-*`) and ensure every interactive element is accessible (`aria-*` attributes and keyboard support).
- Framer Motion is the default choice for complex animations; for simple transitions rely on CSS.
- Components live in `src/components/<Feature>/` with `index.ts` barrel exports.
- Validate incoming props and API responses using `zod` schemas to keep type contracts explicit.
- Use `@tanstack/react-query` for client-side data fetching and caching; mutations should invalidate relevant queries.
- Icons come from `lucide-react` or `@heroicons/react` only.
- Attach stable `data-testid` attributes for E2E tests (Cypress/Playwright).

